    <guid>https://dxing.blog/Algorithms/Extended-Euclidean-Algorithm</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[ The Extended Euclidean Algorithm is an algorithm that finds a pair of integers x and y such that ax+by=\gcd\{a,b\} for non-negative integers a and b in \mathcal{O}(\log a+\log b) time and \mathcal{O}(\log a+\log b) space. ]]></description>
